      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and operating parameters are documented with sources and uncertainty ranges identified.",
      "rationale": "Blood analogue fluid properties (density 1005 kg/m3, dynamic viscosity 0.00119 Pa·s) are sourced from the FDA benchmark protocol. Impeller geometry is derived from the published FDA CAD model. All inputs are tabulated in the simulation report with source references."
